body:
Please check the consumer code, don't modify message body in consumer callback, for example:
```
consumer.registerMessageListener((MessageListenerConcurrently) (msgs, context) -> {
            msgs.get(0).setBody(new byte[0]);
            return ConsumeConcurrentlyStatus.CONSUME_SUCCESS;
        });
```
the msgSize will be wrong in processqueue,  and pull will be ratelimted forever

